Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.03,0:00:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳...妳怎麼了？香草\N有什麼地方不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.97,0:00:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳沒事吧，請振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.04,0:00:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕，再這樣下去\N香草會死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.21,0:00:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，怎...怎麼辦才好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.28,0:00:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒愚蠢的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.35,0:00:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我所犯下的罪過\N我會親自償還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.69,0:00:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.50,0:00:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.84,0:00:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.04,0:00:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危機，這下糟糕了\N緊張！緊張！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.85,0:00:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩光線  BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡鬧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.82,0:01:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒關係，吃個飲茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.63,0:01:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著歡悅的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.79,0:01:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一起向神明祈禱吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.00,0:01:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.53,0:01:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.27,0:01:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它順其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.71,0:01:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有機關，沒有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.15,0:01:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一擲的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無憂無慮的狂歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.95,0:01:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢想與希望的機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.82,0:01:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎖定想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.16,0:01:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧\NBRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.86,0:01:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人興奮的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.47,0:01:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開闢天下無敵的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(遺失物品菜肉濃湯)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.19,0:02:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要開槍？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.26,0:02:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，因為嚇了一跳\N不小心就開槍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會有這種人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.33,0:02:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，妳剛才說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.13,0:02:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...那個...\N香草再這樣下去會死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.23,0:02:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我問妳為什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.73,0:02:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她已經兩個禮拜沒吃東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.50,0:02:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為懺悔而斷食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.21,0:02:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斷食？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.64,0:02:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是兩星期前發生的事\N我和香草一起在街上巡邏時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.45,0:02:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草好像把什麼\N重要的東西給弄丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼東西呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.99,0:02:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那個很重要的東西呀\N香草總是隨身帶著走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那種東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳連這個也不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.84,0:02:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草經常把那個東西\N緊握在手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時也是，那時也是，那時也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.84,0:03:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我問那是什麼東西啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道\N沒看過也沒聽說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.78,0:03:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛才不是一副知道的口氣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只說我知道\N她緊握著什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.46,0:03:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我一句也沒說過\N我知道那個是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.63,0:03:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果把那個東西弄丟了\N在找到之前必須斷食嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.46,0:03:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這樣持續斷食下去\N香草她會....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不快點找到那個東西的話\N香草會死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N是這樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.78,0:03:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，實際上有點困難\N雖然我很想幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.49,0:03:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不知道那個失物是什麼\N那要怎麼找呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.39,0:03:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題\N我們可以去拜託"銀河之母"呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河之母？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.47,0:04:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來介紹...這位是銀河之母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是蘭花嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.58,0:04:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對\N雖然有點像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是占卜師的"銀河之母"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，蘭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河之母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.09,0:04:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.32,0:04:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫她蘭花沒回應\N叫她銀河之母就有回應了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這證明了她不是蘭花喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼證據啊\N喂，蘭花，妳給我醒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在西北方位\N好像坐著一位有困擾的年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.00,0:04:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡有鯨魚居住的海洋\N想找的東西就在那附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.01,0:04:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點也聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西北...西北方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.05,0:04:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有鯨魚噴水池\N煩惱的年輕人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉思者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.08,0:04:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捕鯨街A地區\N那邊也是巡邏的區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能是那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.76,0:05:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果蘭花的占卜可信的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我接受這個尋找失物的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.80,0:05:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命名為"尋找失物小隊"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,LET'S  GO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，等我回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.55,0:05:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，小狗狗，好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，好可怕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.06,0:05:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N請問鯨魚噴水池在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.23,0:05:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？\N我還以為是人，原來是鯨魚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.60,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？原來是這裡呀\N遺失物在哪裡呢...啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.81,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，是這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彩券？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中獎了\N第一特獎5000萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.69,0:06:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.82,0:06:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優真厲害\N香草的失物一定是這個東西啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優的運氣還是一樣好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.96,0:06:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠提前解決，實在太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.94,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.77,0:06:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在搞什麼啊\N怎麼把5000萬給丟了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？香草怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.25,0:06:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？\N找錯東西就沒有意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.59,0:06:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛，我真是的\N找錯東西了還這麼高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊，我真笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.49,0:06:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再去找一遍，銀河之母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.60,0:06:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，對喔，占卜是嗎？\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.77,0:06:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在物慾混沌的河流當中\N螃蟹在蠕動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.34,0:06:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是指繁華街吧\N在五號街有家螃蟹專賣店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那附近的箱子裡\N有個閃閃發光的物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.81,0:07:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我吧，我這就出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.32,0:07:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次一定要找到...\N啊，壞小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.69,0:07:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,箱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.56,0:07:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.97,0:07:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了\N是這個吧，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳又撿到一個不得了的東西耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.37,0:07:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是宇宙紀元前黃金王朝的\N多耶王三世穿戴過的27點首飾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.75,0:07:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中的紅寶石\N單單一個就要八千萬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此，所以才會隨身攜帶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.12,0:07:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，對不起，這麼久才找到\N給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.96,0:07:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在想什麼啊？真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.60,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易可以當上大富翁的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.41,0:08:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又撿錯東西回來了是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.18,0:08:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再去找找\N這次一定會好好找回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.35,0:08:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，她沒聽我的占卜就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.29,0:08:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三次的出發...啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘了問地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就先把那附近掉的東西\N全帶回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，那個不是中國傳說中的\N"天命招魂壺"嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.78,0:08:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說已經不存在在世界上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？值多少錢呢\N不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.89,0:08:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果收藏家知道這還存在的話\N一定價值數億元以上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.49,0:08:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,數億元？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又找錯了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.01,0:09:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，這樣有點過份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄...薄荷，沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好，這種態度不好吧，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.82,0:09:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優這麼努力在幫妳找了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.72,0:09:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，就算找錯了\N也不用著把它丟掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.93,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,努力找東西的梅爾優好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.30,0:09:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣說，我沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不覺得這樣\N梅爾優太可憐了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.34,0:09:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...那個...\N妳還是向她道歉比較好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.44,0:09:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，跟梅爾優道歉，香草\N那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.99,0:09:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.02,0:10:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不要欺負香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.23,0:10:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了，我知道了\N梅爾優不要哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會再罵香草了，別哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.47,0:10:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此大的風波當中\N我拿著吸塵器吸地板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.51,0:10:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許大家會認為我是無情的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是並非如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.38,0:10:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在這種波濤洶湧的心情\N只能靠打掃這方法來分散注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.62,0:10:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起...女孩們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.63,0:10:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草她...香草她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.97,0:10:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為找不到重要的東西\N而心急的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,垃圾塞住了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.21,0:10:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...妳的鼻子都是鼻涕呀\N快把鼻涕擤掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.22,0:11:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，我已經沒事了\N我再去找一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.86,0:11:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個到底是什麼東西啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.47,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說那是信徒\N必須持有的護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.51,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了，找到就好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之，梅爾優辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.78,0:11:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀\N梅爾優那傢伙竟然睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.23,0:11:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下個菜單是  「燒烤盒裝少女」\N佛特是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很會照顧人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最喜歡吃不甜的蘋果派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個很重要的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是宇宙的大英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.58,0:11:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說要頒發名譽勳章給她喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.53,0:12:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.33,0:12:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.67,0:12:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躺在新月下的吊床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.48,0:12:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作了夢之後，變得想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,側耳傾聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.29,0:12:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是聽見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.19,0:12:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人興奮的天線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.27,0:12:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它睡著吧  NO  NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:13:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處女座的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.28,0:13:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向牡羊座的你發出信號\N急電，急電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.35,0:13:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘著飛馬的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去迎接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.59,0:13:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DARING  LOVING  YOU

